    <h2>
        2.1.3 Adding References
    </h2>

    <p>
        To add references to the required modules to your project:
    </p>

    <ul>
        <li>
            Expand your project in the Solution Explorer
        </li>
        <li>
            Right-click 'References' and select 'Add Reference...'
        </li>
        <li>
            Add references to the following modules:
            <br/>
            <img src="../../image/example_refs.png"/>
        </li>
    </ul>

    <h2>
        2.1.4 Adding Lexer Resource Files
    </h2>

    <p>
        To add required lexer resource files to your project:
    </p>

    <ul>
        <li>
            Right-click your project in the Solution Explorer
        </li>
        <li>
            Select 'Add | Existing Item...'
        </li>
        <li>
            Navigate to the <span class="mono">C:\soul-4.0.0\rc</span> folder and add the <span class="mono">soul.xml.xpath.lexer.classmap.rc</span> file to your project.
        </li>
    </ul>

    <h2>
        2.1.5 Compiling the Solution
    </h2>

    <ul>
        <li>Select the <span class="mono">64 | Debug</span> configuration.</li>
        <li>Select the <span class="mono">Build | Build Solution</span> command.</li>
        <li>The required Soul libraries and then your project should compile successfully.</li>
        <li>Select the <span class="mono">64 | Release</span> configuration</li>
        <li>Select the <span class="mono">Build | Build Solution</span> command.</li>
        <li>The required Soul libraries and then your project should compile successfully.</li>
    </ul>

</body>
